## Action Calls

Actions use `@` prefix and call Python functions directly:

- Variable reference: [[@search:results|query=topic,n=5]]
- Literal string: [[@search:results|query="climate change",n=3]]
- Mixed: [[@fetch:content|url=page_url,timeout=30]]
- Positional variable: [[@evidence|topic]]

